; mml2vgm Browser IDE - Hello World Sample
; This is a simple MML file that plays a basic melody
; Format: GWI (mml2vgm format)

; Set up OPNA (YM2608) chip
@OPNA

; Part 0: FM Melody (Channel 0)
@0 v100 l4 o4
@0 c d e f g a b >c2.

; Part 1: FM Bass (Channel 1)
@1 v80 l8 o2
@1 c2. c2. f2. f2. g2. g2. c2.

; Part 2: SSG Drums (Channel 2)
@2 v100 l16 o5
@2 c4 sn4 c4 sn4 c4 c4 sn8 c4 sn4 c4 sn4 c4 c4 sn8
